{
  "title": "Sweet Sticky Middle Eastern Tuna Fattoush",
  "description": "A sweet and gooey Middle Eastern dish featuring tuna, perfect for meal prep, made with ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients in a fattoush form",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
